The reason for the change from Smartdrv.exe 4.0 included with
Windows 3.1 to Smartdrv.exe 4.1 included with DOS 6.0 is
COMPATABILITY WITH DBLSPACE.  Be sure you are running smartdrv from
your DOS directory.
